title.rendered: Jute Roll Rough Style Natural Jute Roll Fabric DIY Craft & Decoration (4.5 Meter) (for Multipurpose use) (Beige Color)

content.rendered: Package Includes : 1 Piece of Jute Roll Color : Natural burlap color Size : 19 Inch 4.5 Meter (5 Yard) This Jute Roll is perfect for most arts, crafts, interior design projects such as table runners, backdrops, matting, costumes, school projects, roman shades, wedding, outside garden, craft projects and much more.
